Protocol of a two arm randomised, multi-centre, 12-month controlled trial: 
evaluating the impact of a Cognitive Behavioural Therapy (CBT)-based 
intervention Supporting UPtake and Adherence to antiretrovirals (SUPA) in adults 
with HIV.

Horne R(1), Glendinning E(2), King K(2), Chalder T(3), Sabin C(4), Walker AS(5), 
Campbell LJ(6), Mosweu I(7), Anderson J(8), Collins S(9), Jopling R(2), McCrone 
