Objective: The objective of this study was to analyze the disease burden of 
influenza in schools and child care settings in rural areas of Hangzhou. 
Methods: Hospital visit influenza cases aged 3-17 years in hospitals that 
reported based on influenza surveillance system from 2016 to 2018 in Chun'an 
county, Hangzhou city were selected as study subjects and a total of 294 
